					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swaghetti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139646); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2139646&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226889" alt="Swaghetti" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2139646)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swaghetti" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2139646); return false;" >Swaghetti</a></span> <span class="odate time_1475238809 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">30 Sep 2016 12:33</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2663223">
									

<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">This&nbsp;was&nbsp;actually&nbsp;supposed&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;one&nbsp;full&nbsp;meta&nbsp;webcomic&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;storyline&nbsp;and&nbsp;everything.&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">This&nbsp;was&nbsp;actually&nbsp;supposed&nbsp;to&nbsp;be&nbsp;one&nbsp;full&nbsp;meta&nbsp;webcomic&nbsp;with&nbsp;a&nbsp;storyline&nbsp;and&nbsp;everything.&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>(Edited to collapse)</p>
<p>It was supposed to be a webcomic about a guy entering a webcomic contest, he then struggles to come up with ideas and ends up drawing a webcomic, called Arthur Page, about the predicament he's in, albeit with slight changes. Namely, the comic (Arthur Page, stay with me) would have been about a struggling sci-fi writer. Who would then write 3 stories and be allowed to create an Author Page and then all sorts of meta-fuckery would consume the universe.</p>
<p>I actually drew the first page as seen here: <a href="http://imgur.com/C9Mw8cN">http://imgur.com/C9Mw8cN</a> But then I realized it would be 6773 pages long.</p>
<p>So I settled with this.</p>
<p>However, if I managed to pull off the actual webcomic&#8230; Well, then I would demand my fucking APOTY award be hand delivered to my personal residence.</p>
</div>
</div>
